\n<br />\n工會Facebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKFUnion%2F&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzmLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=51353023\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/</a><br />\n工會Telegram channel：<a href=\"https://t.me/HKFIEGU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKFIEGU&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzmLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=52f0152d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKFIEGU</a><br />\n<br />\n#特別會員大會"},{"pid":"3fe3ad4a4dee42ab1e993794c2728a3d5b73c22c","tid":1742973,"uid":237425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:26:20.000Z","msg":"將最精銳勇武投放響冇ＧＥＡＲ狗<br />\n陣地戰係盡量避免<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ca5e34e81a172bb2074ee1a2cee3ad8d44be3ec","tid":1742973,"uid":166506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:27:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b228281422b389f865972399844148be73c62beb","tid":1742973,"uid":276150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:28:57.000Z","msg":"係呀每次陣地戰送咗好多娛樂比對家！又打又殺，佢哋覺得有得打活靶好撚過癮！"},{"pid":"5fba3108440723dd3634d95035f23ec43e4469ec","tid":1742973,"uid":276150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:29:57.000Z","msg":"反省下啦點解仲要街頭戰？！應該轉地下。要目標為本，做完就走。"},{"pid":"a513902ad665beda64dc0fbef93701cefae7a5e3","tid":1742973,"uid":276150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:31:46.000Z","msg":"另外就係由於有大量國安入咗嚟香港負責跟蹤，殺人同埋運屍⋯⋯<br />\n我想大家全部都要出街非常alert，要練武術，同埋脫身逃走！"},{"pid":"049d097de1a45d98a033021eb43ee7fa010998c7","tid":1742973,"uid":23482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:47:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8a05c7e16ec5e516ff438e59f72444db9a40a4c1","tid":1742973,"uid":264116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:48:49.000Z","msg":"陣地冇一次贏 仲要損失慘重"},{"pid"